description: Street Food Sensations is serving up the best flavors of the Southwest with their delectable selection of gourmet sandwiches, including the Cubano stuffed with beer-braised pork, apple-wood smoked ham, mustard, pepper jack cheese, pickles, and basil aioli. You are gonna find all their items, including their sides of Parmesan Cilantro Truffle Fries and Green Chile & Bacon Mac Bites to be crazy-tasty. So come eat at this sweet lookin’ truck because their culinary creations are indeed quite sensational.
name: Street Food Sensations
